title: Separated Ain't Single
itunes:title: Separated Ain't Single
description:
Now y'all know Jess is 'bout tired of y'all forcing a relationship between her and Kountry Wayne! In this episode, she gives you the truth about the situation and shares stories of fans who were in similar predicaments. Her twin, Prince, also joined the conversation for a tag-team experience you don't want to miss!
